<MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Safety car</MudText>
<MudDivider Class="my-2" />
<MudText>
    Safety cars may come out after a driver crashes out.
    A crash which caused an injury (or worse) always causes a safey car.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1">Odds</MudText>
<MudText>
    Odds of the safety car coming out (config setting).
    Odds of the safety car coming back in (also configurable).
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1">Tyre wear</MudText>
<MudText>
    Wear is divided by 3, not (yet) configureable.
    A minimum for the remaining tyre life can be configured, by default this is -25.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1">Pitstop</MudText>
<MudText>
    If a tyre has less than half of his original life, then a driver comes in for a
    relatively earlier pit stop.
</MudText>